{"tid":157471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨黨內全數選委將於特首選舉首輪投票支持曾俊華","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T14:22:00.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"641640fa8bea5614da3d4bb45ed51e96ea5f65b7","tid":157471,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"公民黨晚上召開執委會擴大會議，決定黨內全數25名選委於行政長官選舉的第一輪投票中，投票支持候選人曾俊華。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨主席梁家傑會後表示，雖然胡國興的政綱較為代表民主派的價值觀，但觀乎曾俊華與該黨會面及公開論壇的表現，公民黨認為曾俊華是較有能力對抗「西環欽點」，及團結香港的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑說，如果曾俊華當選，公民黨不會鬆懈監察其施政，會嚴格監察他在處理政改及23條立法上，是否有尊重和保證香港人的自由和核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑表示，會尊重胡國興爭取選票的權利。"},{"pid":"e1dedc6c6c224e2992a8b0014fcb4e2a96ee9e24","tid":157471,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"大狀黨首先跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1420ad15a9839b7af315a3170555df0ec801cab","tid":157471,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大狀黨首先跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早已經跟住劇本做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e387a7338467dc1f987b491d8355b62acb3df137","tid":157471,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"3揀1，算係比較明智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd8237f5ab24efbf2e913dce592ba7c3864937","tid":157471,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"泛民對於含撚投票貫徹始終 不論黨或支持者"}]}